A massive blue elephant and a sleek gray wolf facing each other across a polished boardroom table, their reflections visible in the glossy surface. The elephant methodically organizes stacks of paperwork and filing cabinets while the wolf enthusiastically pushes golden coins and treasure maps toward an empty chair between them. The scene is rendered in rich, warm vintage tones reminiscent of 1950s corporate illustrations, with subtle sepia undertones and slightly faded edges. Dramatic overhead lighting casts long shadows across the mahogany table, creating tension between the two contrasting approaches. Small business partner figures—foxes in suits—observe from the doorway, caught between the two giants.
